creator: Mini Sports
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the world of freestyle wrestling it seems to be a real freestyle-wrestling tournament that have different levels of multiple wrestler’s matches. Our latest free wrestling game will give you chance to fight against world superstars in freestyle wrestling championship with HD quality graphics & advanced game play modes. Wrestling game especially designed for professional wrestling lovers. World freestyle wrestling offers multi-man fighting experience in this ultimate wrestling game. Freestyle wrestling game is combines with real multiplayer wrestling actions. Select different wrestlers with advanced fighting styles & techniques. Use special wrestling skills and amazing combo power to take down energy of your rival.


Game Play Modes & Player Selection:
In this Wrestling Rumble fighting sports game, the gameplay is very simple and easy. This wrestling action sports game developed in three amazing & different modes. First, you need to choose your favorite wrestler & than select a Battle Mode. Battle mode consist of three different fighting gameplay modes like Story Mode, Career Mode and Knockout Mode.


Story Mode:
Story mode is all about real life of wrestling stars, behind every fight there is and personal vengeance, which will increase the intensity of rage against rivals in the wrestling ring. First time in the history of wrestling; in Story mode wrestlers personal clashes will converted into the personal fights in different & latest game play challenges.


Career Mode:
In “Career Mode” after every success in fights will earn you some points to unlock next levels. Unlock new fighting challenge. Career mode consists with different & latest sports game play challenges against world wrestling champions. Challenging the next rivals to become the best fighter in this mode.


Knockout Mode:
In “knockout Mode”, fighting mode, which features top wrestlers challenging in different fighting levels. However, keep in mind, no second chance in knockout mode. Knockout match wining will increase the power, intensity, and excitement of real wrestling fights.


Game Wining Rewards:
Earn points for each wining against opponent, fight against strong wrestlers and level up your wrestling skills to get top-level ranking. Upgrade your power, speed, and accuracy with new strikes and fighting styles getting points for each winning match.


Daily Rewards:
In “Daily Rewards Mode”, you will earn bonus points daily that will help you to unlock next players, ultimately getting more points will upgrade power, speed, and accuracy with new strikes and fighting styles. Earing maximum points to unlock next level by watching rewarded videos.

Defeat all freestyle superstar wrestlers in “Story Mode”

Extreme challenging “Knockout Mode” will test your fighting skills

Background music & sound effects will boost your energy

title: Cage Wrestling Fight Game

creator: Mini Sports
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the world of action-adventure games! To be a real wrestler in the wrestling tournaments fight against all the undefeated wrestlers. Our free wrestling games will give you a chance to show your fighting skills and pro wrestle moves. The game offers a multi-man fighting experience in this ultimate wrestling game. This is combined with real multiplayer punch-boxing actions. Select different wrestlers with advanced fighting styles & techniques. Use special skills and amazing combo power to take down the energy of your rival. Be the ultimate brawl super star.


Game Play Modes & Player Selection:

In these cage wrestling games, the play method is very simple and easy. These action wrestling games are developed in three amazing & different modes. First, you need to choose your favorite wrestler & then select a Battle Mode. The brawl version consists of three different fighting gameplay modes like Story, Career, and Knockout.


Story Mode:

The story mode is all about the real-life of wrestling stars, behind every fight there is a personal grudge so pick up where you left off, which will increase the intensity of rage against rivals in the ring. For the first time in the history of wrestling games. in Story mode, wrestlers' clashes will convert into personal fights in different & latest gameplay challenges.


Career Mode:

In “Career Mode” every success in fights will earn you some points to unlock the next levels. Unlock new fighting challenge. Career mode consists of different & latest sports gameplay challenges against world wrestling champions. Challenging the next rivals to become the best fighter in offline wrestling games.


Knockout Mode:

Knockout Mode features top wrestlers challenging in different fighting levels. However, keep in mind, no second chance is given in knockout mode. Knockout match-winning will increase the power, intensity, and excitement of real fighting in the ultimate wrestling games.


Game-Winning Rewards:

Earn points for each winning against an opponent, fight against strong wrestlers, and level up your wrestling skills to get a top-level ranking. The wrestling game is the real one. Upgrade your power, speed, and accuracy with new strikes and fighting styles getting points for each winning match.


Win Daily Rewards:

In “Daily Rewards Mode”, you will earn bonus points daily that will help you to unlock the next players, ultimately getting more points will upgrade power, speed, and accuracy with new strikes and fighting styles. Fight like a champion of the ring. Earning maximum points to unlock the next level by watching rewarded videos. You can play offline fighting games for free.


Cage Wrestling Games: Ring Fighting Champions Features:

• Heavyweight champions fight against world wrestling superstars
• Enjoy three different gameplay mode to test your fighting skills
• Face toughest wrestling warriors and become king of the ring
• Defeat all freestyle superstar wrestlers in “Story Mode”
• Extreme challenging “Knockout Mode” will test your fighting skills
• Real wrestling rivals in action with extreme boxing motions
• Win fight mode matches & get rewarded points to unlock the next challenge
• Background music & sound effects will boost your energy
